high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter with the toaster
Grab the container on the right off of the counter
Turn around and go to the fridge
Cool the container in the fridge and then take it out
Turn left and go to the counter to the right of the sink
Put the container on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting a cold container on the counter

high_descs: Turn right and walk past the refrigerator, then turn left and walk to the bowls on the counter top.
Pick up the bowl on the right.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the bowl in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the bowl on the counter, behind the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled bowl on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn right and walk almost to the sink, but veer left and walk to the counter with the kettle on it.
Pick up the bowl directly behind the kettle on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the bowl on the bottom shelf of the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Place the bowl on the counter to the right and behind the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl on a counter.
